refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
mixedxslt_setopt resourceprocessor intnewmask
xslt_setopt sets the options specified by newmask on the given processor.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the number of previous mask is possible, &true; otherwise,
 &false; in case of an error.

  &reftitle.examples;



    xslt_setopt Example


<?php

$xh = xslt_create();

// Tell Sablotron to process public entities
xslt_setopt($xh, XSLT_SABOPT_PARSE_PUBLIC_ENTITIES);

// Let's also ask it to suppress whitespace stripping
xslt_setopt($xh, xslt_getopt($xh) | XSLT_SABOPT_DISABLE_STRIPPING);

?>
